article.headline: Shumate scores 12 as McNeese takes down Nicholls State 74-47
article.description: — Christian Shumate scored 12 points as McNeese beat Nicholls State 74-47 on Saturday night.
article.linkText: Shumate scores 12 as McNeese takes down Nicholls State 74-47
article.story: THIBODAUX, La. -- — Christian Shumate scored 12 points as McNeese beat Nicholls State 74-47 on Saturday night. Shumate added 12 rebounds for the Cowboys (23-3, 12-1 Southland Conference). Javohn Garcia and DJ Richards added 11 points points apiece. Diante Smith finished with 13 points for the Colonels (13-12, 8-4). Nicholls State also got 10 points from Robert Brown III. In addition, Mekhi Collins had six points and four steals. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
